"title": "8202: boldness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8202",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Courage and confidence in approaching God and also other people.</p>\n<h2>Boldness in approaching God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:19-Heb10:22\">HEB 10:19–10:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:27\">GEN 18:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:31\">GEN 18:31</a> <em>Abraham prays for Sodom</em></p>\n<h2>Boldness in proclaiming the gospel to others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:29\">ACT 4:29</a></strong> <em>Persecuted Christians pray.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:13\">ACT 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:31\">ACT 4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:28\">ACT 9:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:46\">ACT 13:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:3\">ACT 14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:26\">ACT 18:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:8\">ACT 19:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:31\">ACT 28:31</a></p>\n<h2>Boldness in dealing with others</h2>\n<h3>Inner confidence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:3\">PSA 138:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:34-1Sam17:50\">1SA 17:34–17:50</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:1\">PRO 28:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:12\">2CO 3:12</a> <em>Paul concerning his ministry</em></p>\n<h3>Confident authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:8-Phlm1:9\">PHM 1:8–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:15\">ROM 15:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:1-2Cor10:2\">2CO 10:1–10:2</a></p>\n<h3>Courage</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:43\">MRK 15:43</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:8\">EXO 14:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num33:3\">NUM 33:3</a></p>\n<h3>Persistence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:8\">LUK 11:8</a></strong> <em>The friend at midnight.</em></p>\n<h2>Misplaced boldness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:10\">2PE 2:10</a></strong> <em>The heretics' arrogance.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:10\">1CO 8:10</a></p>",
